            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EDavid%20knew%20what%20he%20was%20talking%20about%2C%20for%20he%20had%20faced%20one%20close%20call%20after%20another%20during%20his%20lifetime.%20Near%20the%20end%20of%20his%20life%2C%20he%20faced%20the%20ultimate%20snare%3A%20an%20insurrection%20in%20which%20one%20of%20his%20own%20rebellious%20sons%20attempted%20to%20usurp%20the%20throne%20from%20David's%20chosen%20heir.%20But%20God%20always%20provides%20a%20way%20of%20escape!%20The%20plot%20drew%20the%20attention%20of%20Nathan%2C%20and%20in%20a%20swift%20series%20of%20events%2C%20the%20plan%20of%20the%20rebels%20was%20foiled%20and%20Solomon%20was%20installed%20as%20king.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20apostles%20also%20escaped%20from%20a%20snare%20set%20against%20them.%20The%20Sanhedrin%20rulers%20were%20furious%20with%20the%20apostles%20for%20healing%20the%20cripple.%20They%20purposed%20to%20beat%20them%2C%20jail%20them%2C%20or%20threaten%20them%20in%20some%20way.%20Instead%2C%20the%20Lord%20delivered%20them%2C%20restored%20them%20to%20their%20friends%2C%20and%20filled%20them%20with%20the%20Holy%20Spirit%20(Acts%204%3A23-31).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESatan's%20traps%20and%20snares%20are%20well%20hidden%20and%20powerful%2C%20but%20just%20when%20it%20seems%20his%20plot%20has%20succeeded%2C%20God%20provides%20a%20way%20of%20escape.%20Never%20fear-He'll%20do%20it%20for%20you!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "Kings.1:1-53",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E1%20Kings%201%3A1-53%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_1%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E1%20Kings%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EDavid%20in%20His%20Old%20Age%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EKing%20David%20was%20now%20very%20old%2C%20and%20no%20matter%20how%20many%20blankets%20covered%20him%2C%20he%20could%20not%20keep%20warm.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_2%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20his%20advisers%20told%20him%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BLet%20us%20find%20a%20young%20virgin%20to%20wait%20on%20you%20and%20look%20after%20you%2C%20my%20lord.%20She%20will%20lie%20in%20your%20arms%20and%20keep%20you%20warm.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_3%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20they%20searched%20throughout%20the%20land%20of%20Israel%20for%20a%20beautiful%20girl%2C%20and%20they%20found%20Abishag%20from%20Shunem%20and%20brought%20her%20to%20the%20king.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_4%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20girl%20was%20very%20beautiful%2C%20and%20she%20looked%20after%20the%20king%20and%20took%20care%20of%20him.%20But%20the%20king%20had%20no%20sexual%20relations%20with%20her.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_5%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EAdonijah%20Claims%20the%20Throne%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3EAbout%20that%20time%20David%26%23x2019%3Bs%20son%20Adonijah%2C%20whose%20mother%20was%20Haggith%2C%20began%20boasting%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20will%20make%20myself%20king.%26%23x201D%3B%20So%20he%20provided%20himself%20with%20chariots%20and%20charioteers%20and%20recruited%20fifty%20men%20to%20run%20in%20front%20of%20him.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_6%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3ENow%20his%20father%2C%20King%20David%2C%20had%20never%20disciplined%20him%20at%20any%20time%2C%20even%20by%20asking%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhy%20are%20you%20doing%20that%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20Adonijah%20had%20been%20born%20next%20after%20Absalom%2C%20and%20he%20was%20very%20handsome.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_7%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EAdonijah%20took%20Joab%20son%20of%20Zeruiah%20and%20Abiathar%20the%20priest%20into%20his%20confidence%2C%20and%20they%20agreed%20to%20help%20him%20become%20king.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_8%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20Zadok%20the%20priest%2C%20Benaiah%20son%20of%20Jehoiada%2C%20Nathan%20the%20prophet%2C%20Shimei%2C%20Rei%2C%20and%20David%26%23x2019%3Bs%20personal%20bodyguard%20refused%20to%20support%20Adonijah.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_9%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EAdonijah%20went%20to%20the%20Stone%20of%20Zoheleth%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E1%3A9%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3Eto%20the%20Serpent%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Stone%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20Greek%20version%20supports%20reading%20%3Cem%3EZoheleth%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20a%20proper%20name.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20near%20the%20spring%20of%20En-rogel%2C%20where%20he%20sacrificed%20sheep%2C%20cattle%2C%20and%20fattened%20calves.%20He%20invited%20all%20his%20brothers%26%23x2014%3Bthe%20other%20sons%20of%20King%20David%26%23x2014%3Band%20all%20the%20royal%20officials%20of%20Judah.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_10%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20he%20did%20not%20invite%20Nathan%20the%20prophet%20or%20Benaiah%20or%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20bodyguard%20or%20his%20brother%20Solomon.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_11%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20Nathan%20went%20to%20Bathsheba%2C%20Solomon%26%23x2019%3Bs%20mother%2C%20and%20asked%20her%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BHaven%26%23x2019%3Bt%20you%20heard%20that%20Haggith%26%23x2019%3Bs%20son%2C%20Adonijah%2C%20has%20made%20himself%20king%2C%20and%20our%20lord%20David%20doesn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20even%20know%20about%20it%3F%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_12%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20save%20your%20own%20life%20and%20the%20life%20of%20your%20son%20Solomon%2C%20follow%20my%20advice.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_13%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EGo%20at%20once%20to%20King%20David%20and%20say%20to%20him%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BMy%20lord%20the%20king%2C%20didn%26%23x2019%3Bt%20you%20make%20a%20vow%20and%20say%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BYour%20son%20Solomon%20will%20surely%20be%20the%20next%20king%20and%20will%20sit%20on%20my%20throne%26%23x201D%3B%3F%20Why%20then%20has%20Adonijah%20become%20king%3F%26%23x2019%3B%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_14%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20while%20you%20are%20still%20talking%20with%20him%2C%20I%20will%20come%20and%20confirm%20everything%20you%20have%20said.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_15%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Bathsheba%20went%20into%20the%20king%26%23x2019%3Bs%20bedroom.%20(He%20was%20very%20old%20now%2C%20and%20Abishag%20was%20taking%20care%20of%20him.)%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_16%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EBathsheba%20bowed%20down%20before%20the%20king.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20can%20I%20do%20for%20you%3F%26%23x201D%3B%20he%20asked%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_17%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3EShe%20replied%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BMy%20lord%2C%20you%20made%20a%20vow%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20your%20God%20when%20you%20said%20to%20me%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BYour%20son%20Solomon%20will%20surely%20be%20the%20next%20king%20and%20will%20sit%20on%20my%20throne.%26%23x2019%3B%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_18%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20instead%2C%20Adonijah%20has%20made%20himself%20king%2C%20and%20my%20lord%20the%20king%20does%20not%20even%20know%20about%20it.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22kgs1_1_19%22%20bk%3D%22kgs1%22%20ch%3D%221%22%20vn